sections.heading: fees; clerks of courts; what permitted
sections.text: No filing fees shall be charged by the clerk of any court for any service required by the Nebraska Workers' Compensation Act except as provided in sections 48-138, 48-139, and 48-188.SourceLaws 1935, c. 57, ยง 14, p. 195;C.S.Supp.,1941, ยง 48-175;R.S.1943, ยง 48-1
